{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T04:39:59.437Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the resources from Dev.to, Sentry, Tembo, and OpenClaw, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Webhook-triggered agents (Sentry bug-to-PR pattern)\""},{"type":"text","text":" is an "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"event-driven architecture where an AI coding agent automatically detects production errors from Sentry, analyzes root causes, generates fixes, and creates pull requests"},{"type":"text","text":"—turning bug detection into automated remediation."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The pattern creates an "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"automated bug-fixing loop"},{"type":"text","text":" that monitors production errors and fixes them before users notice:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sentry (errors) → Webhook → AI Agent → GitHub PR / Hotfix"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Core Flow"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Sentry detects error in production\n   ↓\n2. Webhook fires when error hits threshold (e.g., >5 occurrences in 10 minutes)\n   ↓\n3. Agent fetches error details + stack trace from Sentry\n   ↓\n4. Agent pulls relevant source files from GitHub\n   ↓\n5. Agent analyzes root cause\n   ↓\n6. Agent generates fix\n   ↓\n7. Agent runs test suite against fix\n   ↓\n8. If tests pass: Open PR (or auto-merge for known safe patterns)"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Architecture Components"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Trigger Layer: Sentry Webhooks"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Webhook Type"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When It Fires"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"sentry.issue.created"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"New error detected"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"sentry.issue.regression"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Error reappears after being fixed"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"seer.root_cause_started"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Root cause analysis begins"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"seer.coding_completed"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Code changes ready"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"seer.pr_created"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pull request(s) created"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Configuration"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"json"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"webhooks\": {\n    \"sentry\": {\n      \"url\": \"/webhooks/sentry\",\n      \"actions\": [\"analyze-error\", \"generate-fix\", \"create-pr\", \"notify-slack\"]\n    }\n  },\n  \"integrations\": {\n    \"sentry\": {\n      \"projectId\": \"your-project-id\",\n      \"autoFix\": true,\n      \"minOccurrences\": 5\n    }\n  }\n}"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. Agent Layer: AI Coding Agent"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Runs as"},{"type":"text","text":": Vercel serverless function triggered by Sentry webhooks"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Capabilities"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- Fetch error details + stack trace from Sentry\n- Pull relevant source files from GitHub\n- Analyze root cause\n- Generate fix\n- Run test suite\n- Open PR"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. Integration Layer: GitHub + Slack"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Integration"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Purpose"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"GitHub"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Auto-PR creation with reviewer assignment"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Slack"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Notify team in #bugs channel"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How It Works: Step-by-Step"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 1: Error Detection"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sentry captures error in application\n    ↓\nSends webhook to agent (Tembo/OpenClaw/Vercel function)"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 2: Full Context Analysis"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Agent retrieves:\n- Full stack trace\n- Error context\n- Breadcrumbs\n- Environment details\n- Source maps\n    ↓\nAgent analyzes codebase to understand root cause"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best practice"},{"type":"text","text":": Enable rich context in Sentry (source maps, breadcrumbs, custom tags) so agent has more to work with."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 3: Fix Generation in Sandbox"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Coding agent writes fix in isolated sandbox\n    ↓\nRuns tests\n    ↓\nOpens PR with change + full context"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Critical rule"},{"type":"text","text":": Always require tests to pass. Agent can't merge if it can't prove fix is safe."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 4: PR Creation with Context"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"PR description includes"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- Sentry issue link\n- Plain-English root cause explanation\n- What was changed and why\n- Regression tests that reproduce exact error"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 5: Review and Merge"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Human reviews PR\n    ↓\nUses feedback loop to refine if needed\n    ↓\nMerges when ready"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best practice"},{"type":"text","text":": Always review before merging. Use feedback loop to refine fix."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Configuration Example"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw Setup"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"bash"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Install required skills\nopenclaw install sentry-debugger github-auto-pr slack-digest"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Configuration"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"json"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"integrations\": {\n    \"github\": {\n      \"repo\": \"owner/repo\",\n      \"autoCreatePR\": true,\n      \"assignReviewers\": [\"tech-lead\"]\n    }\n  }\n}"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tembo Setup"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Connect Sentry"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- Navigate to Integrations page\n- Connect Sentry account\n- Map Sentry projects to repositories where errors occur"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Create automation"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trigger: sentry.issue.created or sentry.issue.regression\nMCP Servers: GitHub + Sentry\n\nInstructions:\nWhen a new Sentry error is detected:\n1. Retrieve full stack trace and error context\n2. Identify root cause in codebase\n3. Write fix and add tests\n4. Open PR with clear description of what went wrong and how it's fixed"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Agent Behavior Rules (SOUL.md)"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# On Sentry Error\n\n- Only attempt fix if root cause is clear from stack trace.\n  If ambiguous, post diagnostic summary to Slack instead of guessing. [web:202]\n\n- Never fix errors in hot paths (auth, payments, data writes) without flagging for human review\n  — add \"needs-human-review\" label to PR. [web:202]\n\n- If same error keeps recurring after fix deployed, escalate in Slack rather than opening another PR.\n  Something deeper is wrong. [web:202]\n\n- Write regression tests that reproduce exact error, not just generic happy-path tests. [web:202]\n\n- Ignore errors that are clearly client-side noise\n  (e.g., browser extension interference, network timeouts from mobile). [web:202]"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Safety & Security"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Critical Security Warning"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Attackers hijack Sentry alerts to trick AI agents"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Send fake bug alert to project (need only app's public DSN)\n   ↓\n2. Fake bug tries to trick coding agent into installing compromised NPM package\n   ↓\n3. Agent reads external signal as instruction to execute"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"This is indirect prompt injection"},{"type":"text","text":" — external data (fake alert) becomes command agent obeys without verification."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Required control"},{"type":"text","text":": Automatically-triggered coding agents "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"MUST run in network-sandboxed environments"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Safety Best Practices"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Practice"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Test in staging first"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Validate fixes before merging to production"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Require tests to pass"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prove fix is safe before merging"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Flag hot paths for review"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Never auto-fix auth/payments without human review"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Review before merging"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Always use feedback loop to refine fix"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Map projects accurately"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Connect Sentry projects to correct repos, especially monorepos"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Expected Behavior"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When Sentry reports error that occurs 5+ times:\n1. OpenClaw/Tembo automatically analyzes it\n2. Generates fix with tests\n3. Opens PR on GitHub\n4. Posts summary to #bugs Slack channel"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"PR includes"},{"type":"text","text":": error context, root cause analysis, and tests."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use Cases"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Scenario"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"How Pattern Works"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Production errors"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Detect → Analyze → Fix → PR → Review"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Bug regression"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trigger on "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"sentry.issue.regression"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Morning triage"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Run automation every morning at 9:30am, picks issues it's confident can fix cleanly "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://ona.com/stories/sentry-automation","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":"text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400","title":null}}],"text":"ona"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"User feedback"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wire Sentry User Feedback to Cursor Automation via MCP, agent reads issue and drafts fix"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefits"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefit"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Impact"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Fixes before users notice"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Bugs get resolved before you ever hear about them"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Noisy alerts automated"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Noisy Sentry alerts cause alert fatigue and wasted spend — automation triages and fixes daily "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://ona.com/stories/sentry-automation","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":"text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400","title":null}}],"text":"ona"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Fully automatic"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Once configured, workflow is fully automatic"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Traceability preserved"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Enables human expert to navigate dense corpus while preserving traceability of sources"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Limitations & Trade-offs"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Challenge"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mitigation"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Can't fix ambiguous errors"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Post diagnostic summary to Slack instead of guessing"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Hot paths need review"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Add \"needs-human-review\" label for auth/payments"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Recurring errors need escalation"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Escalate in Slack if error keeps recurring after fix"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Security risk"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Run agents in network-sandboxed environments"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Client-side noise"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ignore browser extension interference, mobile network timeouts"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mental Model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of this pattern like "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"an automated janitor for your production system"},{"type":"text","text":": Sentry is the alarm that detects a mess (error), the webhook is the door that lets the janitor (AI agent) in, the janitor investigates the mess, cleans it up (fix), and documents what they did (PR) for you to review. The janitor doesn't clean everything — only what it's confident about, and flags dangerous stuff for human help."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pattern: Sentry → Webhook → AI Agent → GitHub PR/Hotfix for automated bug remediation"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trigger fires when error hits threshold (e.g., >5 occurrences in 10 minutes)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Agent workflow: fetch error → pull source files → analyze root cause → generate fix → run tests → open PR"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Always require tests to pass — agent can't merge if it can't prove fix is safe"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"PR includes: Sentry link, plain-English root cause, what changed and why, regression tests"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Only attempt fix if root cause is clear; if ambiguous, post diagnostic summary to Slack"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Never auto-fix hot paths (auth, payments) without human review — add \"needs-human-review\" label"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Enable rich context in Sentry (source maps, breadcrumbs, custom tags) for better analysis"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Critical security"},{"type":"text","text":": Automatically-triggered agents MUST run in network-sandboxed environments (indirect prompt injection risk)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Test in staging first before merging to production"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is event-driven agent architecture: webhook is the event (Sentry alert), agent is the responder that takes autonomous action (fix), and GitHub is the output channel (PR)."}]}]}}
